Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:56.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}那么就折一架纸飞机 一起踏上旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.17,0:00:00.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得·杜拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素有"管理学之父"之称的管理大师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其著作《管理学》被誉为现代管理人的“圣经”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片所讲述的便是一位高中女生运用《管理学》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中的知识将其平凡无奇的棒球部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带入夏季甲子园的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:06.17,ti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,450)}{\fad(800,0)}南为高中棒球所感动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪恢复了以往和蔼的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一个人在 战斗着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪她 终于去到了没有病魔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人出局 满垒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪离开了我们 应该感到悲伤才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却无法按捺住 涌上心头的这股情感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 浅野君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1棒 左外野手 田村君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球打出去 田村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2棒 中外野手 柳泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 田村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一口气把局面逆转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 浅野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思议的 疲劳都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像是夕纪在身边一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星出君 状态没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是恐怕星出君会被保送的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星出今天击出了2支安打状态很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一垒空着的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会采取比较安全的策略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 明明是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是要保送他上垒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手保送了星出要和你较量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就让他们好好后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天因为夕纪去世 我明明一点觉都没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然感觉不到疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉 会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 三分本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.89,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：スリーラン，出自three-run homer，指一次得三分的本垒打。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6棒 游击手 樱井君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐之助 继续拿分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得把祐之助撤下先发名单比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会输掉比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为相信祐之助的成长并让他上场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是管理学应该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐之助 把球打出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人出局 攻防转换
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪 你在看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力地向着甲子园拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年甲子园对大家来说还只是个遥不可及的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们相信着我们的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力地拼搏着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9局后半 两人出局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4棒 三垒手 星出君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手在防备你的本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手在防备我的长打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内野手也退得更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全触击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.02,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*注：安全触击，打者为了让自己能够成功上一垒而采取的触击方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 星出君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全骗过了对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是无触击战术就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不喜欢自我牺牲的触击球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个触击球却是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5棒 捕手 柏木君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想逃避了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为柏木在之前击出过本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送也是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备与到目前为止无安打的祐之助一决胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二阶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练 要把祐之助换下场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我并不是要换下他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也说过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是棒球部不可或缺的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是要我下课我也不会换下他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程久保高中换人通知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑者 由朽木替换柏木上场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送柏木这一决定 我会让他们后悔一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球保送也有不适用的场合这一崭新的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要在此让他们见识下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的 朽木君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你居然回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然来看我们的比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 文乃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被文乃指责了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我不要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说你能来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来的话可就没人带领我们去甲子园了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把注意力都集中在打者身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个缺乏抗压能力的祐之助君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一球就积极挥棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样挥大棒是打不到球的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加盯紧球路才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样挥大棒是打不到球的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加盯紧球路才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是在空挥之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很担心你打不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个球从左半场中间飞出去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有生以来第一次体验到那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋和感动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木学长 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生还 比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.72,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*注：生还，安全回到本垒。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 夕纪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪你当时所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有逃避真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做经理真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与管理学相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做市场调查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致力于社会贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过自我目标管理进行练习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家从那时起就以打进甲子园为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致力于高中棒球的创新
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和祐之助说过了吗 那时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在探病面谈的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那是作为我喜欢上棒球的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而无法忘记的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这里开始插入ED歌词和译文，ED以今晚发送的为准，有补充）
